# Supabase
# IMPORTANT: The following should be TRACKED in Git:
#   - supabase/config.toml (configuration)
#   - supabase/migrations/ (migration files)
#   - supabase/seed.sql (seed data)
# The following are auto-ignored via supabase/.gitignore:
#   - supabase/.temp/ (CLI temporary files)
#   - supabase/.branches/ (local branch data)
supabase_backup_*
